{"title_page": "Harendra Kumar Sur", "text_new": "'''Harendra Kumar Sur''' was a Member of the [[List of members of the 1st National Assembly of Pakistan|1st National Assembly of Pakistan]] as a representative of East Pakistan.\n\n==Career==\nSur represented Noakhali in the Bengal Legislative Council.<ref>{{cite book |last1=Chatterjee |first1=Srilata |title=Congress Politics in Bengal 1919-1939 |date=2003 |publisher=Anthem Press |isbn=978-1-84331-366-3 |page=182 |url=https://books.google.com.bd/books?id=2L81DgAAQBAJ&pg=PA182&dq=Harendra+Kumar+Sur&hl=en&sa=X&ved=0ahUKEwjQzYbbiIPpAhWKfn0KHYQEAvYQ6AEIJTAA#v=onepage&q=Harendra%20Kumar%20Sur&f=false |language=en}}</ref> He was a member of the [[Constituent Assembly of Pakistan]].<ref>{{cite book |title=Constituent Assembly of Pakistan Debates: Official Report |date=1950 |publisher=Manager of Publications. |page=114 |url=https://books.google.com.bd/books?id=YeAanEgiD4cC&q=Harendra+Kumar+Sur&dq=Harendra+Kumar+Sur&hl=en&sa=X&ved=0ahUKEwjQzYbbiIPpAhWKfn0KHYQEAvYQ6AEILjAB |language=en}}</ref>\n\n==Death==\nSur died in 1964.<ref>{{cite book |title=Calcutta Municipal Gazette |date=1964 |publisher=Office of the Registrar of Newspapers. Press in India |page=39 |url=https://books.google.com.bd/books?id=DLXFScQ__q0C&q=%22Harendra+Kumar+Sur%22+died&dq=%22Harendra+Kumar+Sur%22+died&hl=en&sa=X&ved=0ahUKEwiC_qDUlIPpAhXIZSsKHebBDAIQ6AEINDAC |language=en}}</ref>\n\n==References==\n{{Reflist}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Sur}}\n[[Category:Pakistani MNAs 1947\u20131954]]\n[[Category:1964 deaths]]\n", "text_old": "'''Harendra Kumar Sur''' was a Member of the [[List of members of the 1st National Assembly of Pakistan|1st National Assembly of Pakistan]] as a representative of East Pakistan.\n\n==Career==\nSur represented Noakhali in the Bengal Legislative Council.<ref>{{cite book |last1=Chatterjee |first1=Srilata |title=Congress Politics in Bengal 1919-1939 |date=2003 |publisher=Anthem Press |isbn=978-1-84331-366-3 |page=182 |url=https://books.google.co